==名字==
和大部分韩国人不同，高约翰并没有汉字名，只能写成“{{lang|ko|고요한}}<ref>[http://www.kleague.com/kr/sub.asp?avan=1006020000&clubInfoMode=player_info&iptPlayerid=20040082 {{lang|ko|현대오일뱅크 K리그 클래식 - Talk About K LEAGUE}}] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305025031/http://www.kleague.com/kr/sub.asp?avan=1006020000&clubInfoMode=player_info&iptPlayerid=20040082 |date=2016-03-05 }}</ref>”。他的名字“{{lang|ko|요한}}”来自《[[圣经|圣经]]》中[[耶稣|耶稣]]的使徒[[約翰_(使徒)|約翰]]的韩语音译。部分华语媒体则译成高尧韩。

